data.description: Above average in size and quality! This almost 1800 SqFt home lives like a 4 Bedroom and has 3 full bathrooms! The two story addition to this Oak Manor floorplan transforms this home into an ideal multi family or multi generational gem. Two master bedrooms with ensuite bathrooms give this home it's flexibility. One of the suites is on the second story, up a fun spiral staircase. With nice updates throughout, and the most convenient location, come get one of the best price per sqft deals in Ukiah!
